LUMI.BUDDY 8051
Copyright 2026 LUMI.BUDDY contributors

This package contains an original course project implementation for an
8051/STC89C52-compatible board and LCD12864 display.

Anthropic Claude Desktop Buddy is referenced only as design inspiration.
No Claude Desktop Buddy source code or assets are included.

Course handout PDFs, private notes, backups, and personal evidence files
are intentionally excluded from this package.
